pokedexEntries.red: Although its fur has many admirers, it is tough to raise as a pet because of its fickle meanness.
pokedexEntries.blue: Although its fur has many admirers, it is tough to raise as a pet because of its fickle meanness.
pokedexEntries.yellow: The gem in its forehead glows on its own! It walks with all the grace and elegance of a proud queen.
pokedexEntries.gold: Many adore it for its sophisticated air. However, it will lash out and scratch for little reason.
pokedexEntries.silver: Its lithe muscles allow it to walk without making a sound. It attacks in an instant.
pokedexEntries.crystal: Behind its lithe, elegant appearance lies a barbaric side. It will tear apart its prey on a mere whim.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Persian has six bold whiskers that give it a look of toughness. The whiskers sense air movements to determine what is in the Pokémon's surrounding vicinity. It becomes docile if grabbed by the whiskers.
pokedexEntries.sapphire: Persian has six bold whiskers that give it a look of toughness. The whiskers sense air movements to determine what is in the Pokémon's surrounding vicinity. It becomes docile if grabbed by the whiskers.
pokedexEntries.emerald: A Persian's six bold whiskers sense air movements to determine what is in its vicinity. It becomes docile if grabbed by the whiskers.
pokedexEntries.fireRed: Has a vicious temperament. Beware if it raises its tail straight up. It is a signal that it is about to pounce and bite.
pokedexEntries.leafGreen: Although its fur has many admirers, it is tough to raise as a pet because of its fickle meanness.
pokedexEntries.diamond: A very haughty Pokémon. Among fans, the size of the jewel in its forehead is a topic of much talk.

pokedexEntries.sun: It has a violent temperament. It will attack anything that looks it in the eye. Its sharp claws inflict deep wounds.
pokedexEntries.moon: It has a high opinion of itself, although not to the same extent as the Alolan Persian. It's quite difficult to make friends with this Pokémon.
pokedexEntries.ultraSun: Although the jewel on its forehead appears to be a different color than those of Alolan Persian, it’s mostly made of the same material.
pokedexEntries.ultraMoon: This Pokémon is popular with rich people. It’s also targeted by hunters who are after the jewel in its forehead.
